headline.main: Britain Urges Kenya to Restore Order After Rancher Killed
headline.print_headline: Britain Urges Kenya to Restore Order After Rancher Killed

lead_paragraph: Britain on Monday urged Kenya to restore law and order in the north of the country after a British rancher was shot dead there.
